                <StackPanel Margin="20">
                    <!-- Title -->
                    <TextBlock FontSize="24" FontWeight="Bold" Text="Lesson 1: Personal Pronouns in Russian" Margin="0,0,0,20" TextAlignment="Center"/>

                    <!-- Introduction -->
                    <TextBlock FontSize="20" Text="Introduction" FontWeight="Bold" Margin="0,0,0,10"/>
                    <TextBlock FontSize="18" TextWrapping="Wrap">
                In this lesson, you will learn about personal pronouns in Russian. Personal pronouns are used to refer to specific people or things. Understanding these pronouns is essential for constructing sentences and communicating effectively in Russian.
                    </TextBlock>

                    <!-- Personal Pronouns Table -->
                    <TextBlock FontSize="20" Text="Personal Pronouns" FontWeight="Bold" Margin="20,20,0,10"/>
                    <Grid Margin="0,0,0,20">
                        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                            <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
